DEPENDENCIES (and setup instruction)

DansGuardian >=  2.12

Squid3

SQLAUTH PATCH/FORK:

http://tech.groups.yahoo.com/group/dansguardian/message/24647

https://github.com/gderosa/dansguardian

ANTIVIRUS:

Currently only clamd is supported.

ClamD must be able to access DG temporary files, so you have to do something
like:

  adduser clamav dansguardian

and restart clamD

GEMS

gem install dansguardian

